creating centrailize state of app in store
    1. Creating to do Class.
        properties --> id, text, status
    2. Create collection/array list of to do's 
        properties - todo list
        add methods on class 
            1. add a todo 
            2. remove todo
            3. change to do data.       
    3. when refreshing the page will empty the list.   
    4. store should be immutable.    

Presentational layer should render on document on documentid
    1. add component button which will add values to store
    2. remove button remove